Also at that time, there's still has no intention of mine to study about the members or even want to know every single name of them. And now in November 2021, I'm binge-watching their GoSe episodes and even know half-everything about them cuz I'm starting to study them hehe till I'm nowadays very attached to Mingyu and Wonwoo and sometimes (but always actually hehe) attracted to Seungkwan and Jeonghan. To conclude Im SICK, ALONE, AND STRESSED OUT. but smhow i have that one instinct to open YouTube tonight, and when i did, pledis just release this: our long awaited part switch ver. and the moment i hear the harmonized seventeen at the very start of the vidoe. i cry. i miss them so much. i acted tough for so long and when Verkwan happen (my fav otp) i smiled. ğŸ˜„ and god it feels great to smile again and laugh at these dorks. Thank you my lil babies ğŸ’•you made my day more then i can express it in words.
